snippet.title: Football Manager 2021: Xbox Edition | Play it Now
snippet.description: The world’s favorite football management game returns to console for the first time in over a decade. FM21: Xbox Edition thrusts you onto the big stage with a bespoke version of the game carefully crafted for effortless performance with the Xbox controller.
